                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7981" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1243</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1902 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">想说爱你不容易：科华合并天隆过程中的子公司失控</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">It’s Not Easy to Say I Love You——Losing Control over Subsidiaries in the Process of Kehua Bio-Engineering Merging Tianlong Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宇恒，吴逸婷，陆祎祺，徐章铭</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海科华生物工程股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业合并；控制；子公司失控；会计处理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business combination;Control;Losing control over subsidiaries;Accounting treatment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年，作为国内第一家上市的体外诊断企业，科华生物为加强在分子诊断这一细分领域的战略布局，收购了强势分子诊断企业天隆公司62%的股权，并与之签订了剩余38%股份的收购要约。可是由于进一步并购条款存在隐患，新冠疫情期间，科华生物与其子公司天隆公司爆发了百亿股权转让纠纷，母公司所持全部股权惨遭冻结，股东权利也被禁止行使，其股票被实施“退市风险警示”，众多股东蒙受不赀之损。几经波折，科华生物最终于2022年对天隆公司实现复控。本案例回顾了科华生物对天隆公司“控制、失控、复控”的三个阶段，重点描述了科华生物失去天隆公司控制权的过程，旨在引导学生从企业会计准则的视角判断控制的三要素、辨析子公司失控的会计处理方法、分析“控制权+剩余股权”两步走全资收购子公司模式的优劣势、思考降低并购风险的应对措施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2018, as the first listed in vitro diagnostic company in China, Kehua Bio-Engineering acquired 62% equity of Tianlong Company, a leading molecular diagnostic company, and signed a purchase offer for the remaining 38% equity in order to strengthen its strategic layout in the niche field of molecular diagnosis. However, due to potential risks of further merger and acquisition terms, these two companies broke out a 10 billion yuan equity transfer dispute during the COVID-19 epidemic, resulting in the freezing of all shares held, the prohibition of shareholders&#39; rights, and the implementation of a delisting risk warning for stocks, causing huge damage to shareholders&#39; interests. After several twists and turns, Kehua Bio-Engineering finally regained control over Tianlong Company in 2022. This case reviews three stages of gaining, losing and regaining control over subsidiary with a focus on the process of losing control. It aims to guide students to determine the three elements of control from the perspective of corporate accounting standards, identify the accounting treatments of subsidiaries out of control, analyze the advantages and disadvantages of the two-step mode of &quot;control right + remaining equity&quot; to fully-acquire subsidiaries, and consider countermeasures to reduce risks of mergers and acquisitions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实质重于形式；委托代理理论；并购风险；风险传染理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
